text: The Winn-Dixie Jacksonville Open was a golf tournament on the Web.com Tour from 2010 to 2012. It was played for the first time in October 2010 at TPC Sawgrass's Dye's Valley Course in Ponte Vedra Beach, Florida.Nationwide Tour heading to TPC Sawgrass in 2010 The 2012 purse was US$600,000, with $108,000 going to the winner. ==Winners== {|class=wikitable style=font-size:95% !Year!!Winner!!Country!!Score!!To par!!Margin of victory!!Runner(s)-up |- | 2012 || Russell Henley || || align=center|270 || align=center|−10 || Playoff || B.
